OL,3,CBudget will 'embrace harsh light of
OL,4,Cfiscal reality', Starmer to say in
OL,5,Cspeech
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer will say this week's
OL,8,FBudget will embrace the "harsh light
OL,9,Fof fiscal reality" but "better days
OL,10,Fare ahead", in a speech ahead of one
OL,11,Fof the most significant financial
OL,12,Fstatements in recent history.
OL,14,FThe prime minister will warn of
OL,15,F"unprecedented" economic challenges
OL,16,Fand invite the public to judge him on
OL,17,Fhis ability to rise to them as he sets
OL,18,Fthe tone for Wednesday's announcement.
