OL,4,Cfiscal reality', Starmer to say in
OL,5,Cspeech
OL,7,FReferring to the statements announced
OL,8,Fby New Labour's Gordon Brown and
OL,9,Fausterity-era Conservative chancellor
OL,10,FGeorge Osborne, Sir Keir will say: "We
OL,11,Fhave to be realistic about where we
OL,12,Fare as a country. This is not 1997,
OL,13,Fwhen the economy was decent but public
OL,14,Fservices were on their knees.
OL,16,F"And it's not 2010, where public
OL,17,Fservices were strong, but the public
OL,18,Ffinances were weak. These are
OL,19,Funprecedented circumstances.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
