OL,3,CBudget will 'embrace harsh light of
OL,4,Cfiscal reality', Starmer to say in
OL,5,Cspeech
OL,7,F"And that's before we even get to the
OL,8,Flong-term challenges ignored for 14
OL,9,Fyears: an economy riddled with
OL,10,Fweakness on productivity and
OL,11,Finvestment, a state that needs urgent
OL,12,Fmodernisation to face down the
OL,13,Fchallenge of a volatile world."
OL,15,FThe prime minister is expected to say
OL,16,Fhe will not offer the UK's problems as
OL,17,F"an excuse", adding: "I won't offer it
OL,18,Fas an excuse. I expect to be judged on
OL,19,Fmy ability to deal with this.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
