OL,3,CBudget will 'embrace harsh light of
OL,4,Cfiscal reality', Starmer to say in
OL,5,Cspeech
OL,7,F"Politics is always a choice. It's
OL,8,Ftime to choose a clear path, and
OL,9,Fembrace the harsh light of fiscal
OL,10,Freality so we can come together behind
OL,11,Fa credible, long-term plan."
OL,13,FIt comes amid opposition accusations
OL,14,Fof hypocrisy over an expected decision
OL,15,Fto extend a freeze on income tax
OL,16,Fthresholds introduced under the
OL,17,FTories, and confusion over the Labour
OL,18,Fgovernment's use of the term of
OL,19,F"working people".
