OL,7,FCombined with a hike in the rate of
OL,8,Femployer contributions, this is
OL,9,Fexpected to raise around #20 billion
OL,10,Fas Ms Reeves seeks to revive public
OL,11,Fservices and put the economy on a
OL,12,Ffirmer footing.
OL,14,FSome #1.4 billion has been announced
OL,15,Falready to rebuild crumbling schools,
OL,16,Fas well as a tripling of investment in
OL,17,Ffree breakfast clubs, #1.8 billion for
OL,18,Fthe expansion of government-funded
OL,19,Fchildcare, and #44 million to support
OL,20,Fkinship and foster carers.
