OL,7,FMinisters have vowed there will be no
OL,8,Freturn to austerity, but Ms Reeves is
OL,9,Funderstood to have called on
OL,10,Fgovernment departments to make
OL,11,Fefficiency savings of 2% in order to
OL,12,Ffree up "billions" of pounds that
OL,13,Fwould be reinvested in the front line.
OL,15,FThe chancellor will also announce a
OL,16,Fchange to the UK's debt rule that will
OL,17,Fopen the door for the government to
OL,18,Fspend billions more on long-term
OL,19,Finfrastructure, such as replacing
OL,20,Fdilapidated buildings on the public
OL,21,Fsector estate.
