OL,7,FShe is expected to target public
OL,8,Fsector net financial liabilities
OL,9,F(PSNFL) as her new measure of debt
OL,10,Frather than the current yardstick of
OL,11,Funderlying public sector net debt.
OL,13,FA shift to PSNFL would give her
OL,14,Fgreater headroom to meet her debt
OL,15,Freduction target, because it includes
OL,16,Fa wider mix of state assets and
OL,17,Fliabilities - notably including
OL,18,Fexpected student loan repayments to
OL,19,Foffset some of the liability.
